"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-24-rules-whipping-horses-dressage-charlotte-dujardin-withdraws-olympics-21285867\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Charlotte Dujardin has withdrawnfrom Team GB for theParisOlympicsafter avideo emerged of her whipping a horsein a coaching session, but what are the rules for using whips in dressage?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 183, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charlotte Dujardin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"withdrawnfrom Team GB\", \"from\": 23, \"to\": 44}, {\"ngram\": \"theParisOlympicsafter avideo\", \"from\": 49, \"to\": 77}, {\"ngram\": \"a horsein\", \"from\": 102, \"to\": 111}, {\"ngram\": \"a coaching session\", \"from\": 112, \"to\": 130}, {\"ngram\": \"the rules\", \"from\": 145, \"to\": 154}, {\"ngram\": \"whips\", \"from\": 165, \"to\": 170}, {\"ngram\": \"dressage\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When competing in dressage, entering the arena with a whip is against the rules and will result in a technical fault.\", \"from\": 185, \"to\": 302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"dressage\", \"from\": 203, \"to\": 211}, {\"ngram\": \"the arena\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 231}, {\"ngram\": \"a whip\", \"from\": 237, \"to\": 243}, {\"ngram\": \"the rules\", \"from\": 255, \"to\": 264}, {\"ngram\": \"a technical fault\", \"from\": 284, \"to\": 301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, whips are allowed to be used in the practice area, as long as it is dropped before entering the space around the competition arena.\", \"from\": 304, \"to\": 444, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"whips\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 318}, {\"ngram\": \"the practice area\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 362}, {\"ngram\": \"the space\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 414}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition arena\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 443}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Federation for Equestrian Sports (FEI) state in their rules on whips: 'At all international Events, it is forbidden to carry a whip of any kind while competing in the arena.\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 498, \"end\": 501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.075814727842047e-40, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The International Federation\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 474}, {\"ngram\": \"their rules\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 523}, {\"ngram\": \"whips\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 532}, {\"ngram\": \"all international Events\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 562}, {\"ngram\": \"a whip\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 595}, {\"ngram\": \"any kind\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 607}, {\"ngram\": \"the arena\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the use of one (1) whip, with a total maximum length of one meter and twenty (1.20 m) (pony Competitions maximum one meter -1 m-), in the practice area is allowed.\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 810, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the use\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 654}, {\"ngram\": \"one (1) whip\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 670}, {\"ngram\": \"a total maximum length\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 699}, {\"ngram\": \"one meter\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 712}, {\"ngram\": \"pony Competitions\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 751}, {\"ngram\": \"the practice area\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The whip must be dropped before entering the space around the Competition arena or the Athlete will be penalized.\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 924, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The whip\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 819}, {\"ngram\": \"the space\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 861}, {\"ngram\": \"the Competition arena\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 890}, {\"ngram\": \"the Athlete\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Upon arrival on the showground, only the Athlete when riding, walking in hand, leading or lunging a Horse (lunge whip allowed), is allowed to use a whip (maximum one meter and twenty (1.20) / ponies maximum one (1) meter in connection with the training of theHorse.\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 1192, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"arrival\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 939}, {\"ngram\": \"the showground\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"only the Athlete\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 975}, {\"ngram\": \"hand\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1004}, {\"ngram\": \"a Horse (lunge whip\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1044}, {\"ngram\": \"a whip\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1079}, {\"ngram\": \"maximum one meter\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1098}, {\"ngram\": \"maximum one (1) meter\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1147}, {\"ngram\": \"connection\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1161}, {\"ngram\": \"the training\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1179}, {\"ngram\": \"theHorse\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1191}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The groom may also walk, lead and lunge a Horse as above.\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1250, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The groom\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1202}, {\"ngram\": \"a Horse\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other parties are allowed to carry a whip, provided it is not in connection with the training of the Horse.\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1358, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Other parties\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1264}, {\"ngram\": \"a whip\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1292}, {\"ngram\": \"connection\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1326}, {\"ngram\": \"the training\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1344}, {\"ngram\": \"the Horse\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1357}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For safety reasons, whips at prize-giving ceremonies are allowed.'\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1425, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"safety reasons\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1377}, {\"ngram\": \"whips\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"prize-giving ceremonies\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the FEI has extensive rules on the welfare of horses and states that any abuse of the animal with a whip is unacceptable.\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1557, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1440, \"end\": 1443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.075814727842047e-40, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"extensive rules\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1463}, {\"ngram\": \"the welfare\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1478}, {\"ngram\": \"horses\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1488}, {\"ngram\": \"states\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1499}, {\"ngram\": \"any abuse\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1514}, {\"ngram\": \"the animal\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1528}, {\"ngram\": \"a whip\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The FEI Code of Conduct states: 'The FEI requires all those involved in international equestrian sport to adhere to the FEI Code of Conduct and to acknowledge and accept that at all times the welfare of the Horse must be paramount.\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1790, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1596, \"end\": 1599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.075814727842047e-40, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 1645, \"end\": 1655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9991355370278743, \"rank\": 0.0008652109147075629, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The FEI Code\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1571}, {\"ngram\": \"Conduct\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1582}, {\"ngram\": \"the FEI Code\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1687}, {\"ngram\": \"Conduct\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1698}, {\"ngram\": \"all times\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1746}, {\"ngram\": \"the welfare\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1758}, {\"ngram\": \"the Horse\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1771}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Welfare of the Horse must never be subordinated to competitive or commercial influences.'\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1882, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Welfare\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1800}, {\"ngram\": \"the Horse\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1813}, {\"ngram\": \"competitive or commercial influences\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1880}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The relevant rule on whips reads: 'Abuse of a Horse using natural riding aids or artificial aids (e.g.\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 1986, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The relevant rule\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 1901}, {\"ngram\": \"whips\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1910}, {\"ngram\": \"a Horse\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1935}, {\"ngram\": \"natural riding aids\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1961}, {\"ngram\": \"artificial aids\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1980}]}, {\"sentence\": \"whips, spurs, etc.)\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 2006, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"whips\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 1992}, {\"ngram\": \"spurs\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 1999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"will not be tolerated.'\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2030, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"An FEI statement on the Dujardin video read: 'The FEI condemns any conduct contrary to the welfare of horses and has robust rules in place to address such behaviour.\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2035, \"end\": 2038, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.075814727842047e-40, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 2082, \"end\": 2085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.075814727842047e-40, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Dujardin video read\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2075}, {\"ngram\": \"any conduct\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2106}, {\"ngram\": \"the welfare\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2130}, {\"ngram\": \"horses\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2140}, {\"ngram\": \"robust rules\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2161}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2170}, {\"ngram\": \"such behaviour\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2196}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our commitment to ensuring the highest standards of equine welfare and sportsmanship remains unwavering.'\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2303, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our commitment\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2212}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest standards\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2246}, {\"ngram\": \"equine welfare\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2264}, {\"ngram\": \"sportsmanship\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"FEI President Ingmar De Vos said: 'We are deeply disappointed with this case, especially as we approach the Olympic Games in Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2441, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2305, \"end\": 2308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.075814727842047e-40, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 2319, \"end\": 2332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ingmar_De_Vos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ingmar De Vos\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ingmar_De_Vos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ingmar_De_Vos\"}, {\"begin\": 2430, \"end\": 2440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4484487925380568e-17, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this case\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2381}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2426}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, it is our responsibility and crucial that we address any instances of abuse, as equine welfare cannot be compromised.\", \"from\": 2442, \"to\": 2568, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our responsibility\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2475}, {\"ngram\": \"any instances\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2517}, {\"ngram\": \"abuse\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2526}, {\"ngram\": \"equine welfare\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Charlotte has expressed genuine remorse for her actions, and we recognise and appreciate her willingness to take responsibility.\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2699, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2571, \"end\": 2580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_49ers\", \"score\": 0.8057330721653692, \"rank\": 0.19592991900904483, \"text\": \"Charlotte\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_49ers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_49ers\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"genuine remorse\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2610}, {\"ngram\": \"her actions\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2626}, {\"ngram\": \"her willingness\", \"from\": 2660, \"to\": 2675}, {\"ngram\": \"responsibility\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2698}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the unfortunate timing, we believe this action reaffirms the FEI's commitment to welfare as the guardians of our equine partners and the integrity of our sport.'\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2869, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2769, \"end\": 2772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.075814727842047e-40, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the unfortunate timing\", \"from\": 2708, \"to\": 2730}, {\"ngram\": \"this action\", \"from\": 2743, \"to\": 2754}, {\"ngram\": \"welfare\", \"from\": 2789, \"to\": 2796}, {\"ngram\": \"the guardians\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2813}, {\"ngram\": \"our equine partners\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 2836}, {\"ngram\": \"the integrity\", \"from\": 2841, \"to\": 2854}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2867}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dujardin's statement read: 'A video has emerged from four years ago which shows me making an error of judgement during a coaching session.\", \"from\": 2871, \"to\": 3009, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dujardin's statement\", \"from\": 2871, \"to\": 2891}, {\"ngram\": \"A video\", \"from\": 2899, \"to\": 2906}, {\"ngram\": \"an error\", \"from\": 2961, \"to\": 2969}, {\"ngram\": \"judgement\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 2982}, {\"ngram\": \"a coaching session\", \"from\": 2990, \"to\": 3008}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Understandably, the International Federation for Equestrian Sports (FEI) is investigating and I have made the decision to withdraw from all competition - including the Paris Olympics - while this process takes place.\", \"from\": 3011, \"to\": 3228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3080, \"end\": 3083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.075814727842047e-40, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the International Federation\", \"from\": 3028, \"to\": 3056}, {\"ngram\": \"Equestrian Sports\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3078}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 3118, \"to\": 3130}, {\"ngram\": \"all competition\", \"from\": 3148, \"to\": 3163}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 3176, \"to\": 3194}, {\"ngram\": \"this process\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3215}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 3222, \"to\": 3227}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'What happened was completely out of character and does not reflect how I train my horses or coach my pupils, however there is no excuse.\", \"from\": 3230, \"to\": 3367, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"character\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3276}, {\"ngram\": \"my horses\", \"from\": 3310, \"to\": 3319}, {\"ngram\": \"my pupils\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3338}, {\"ngram\": \"no excuse\", \"from\": 3357, \"to\": 3366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am deeply ashamed and should have set a better example in that moment.'\", \"from\": 3368, \"to\": 3441, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a better example\", \"from\": 3408, \"to\": 3424}, {\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 3428, \"to\": 3439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stephan Wensing, a Dutch equine lawyer, filed a complaint of animal cruelty against Dujardin while acting on behalf of an anonymous client who was at the training event where the footage was filmed.\", \"from\": 3443, \"to\": 3641, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3443, \"end\": 3450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archduke_Charles_Stephen_of_Austria\", \"score\": 0.5897300033905526, \"rank\": 0.6944375663183071, \"text\": \"Stephan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archduke_Charles_Stephen_of_Austria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archduke_Charles_Stephen_of_Austria\"}, {\"begin\": 3462, \"end\": 3467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.6697178105036151, \"rank\": 0.48459255024725384, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a complaint\", \"from\": 3489, \"to\": 3500}, {\"ngram\": \"animal cruelty\", \"from\": 3504, \"to\": 3518}, {\"ngram\": \"Dujardin\", \"from\": 3527, \"to\": 3535}, {\"ngram\": \"behalf\", \"from\": 3552, \"to\": 3558}, {\"ngram\": \"an anonymous client\", \"from\": 3562, \"to\": 3581}, {\"ngram\": \"the training event\", \"from\": 3593, \"to\": 3611}, {\"ngram\": \"the footage\", \"from\": 3618, \"to\": 3629}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was a sponsored guest lesson, of which my client was the sponsor and went to watch.\", \"from\": 3643, \"to\": 3730, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sponsored guest lesson\", \"from\": 3651, \"to\": 3675}, {\"ngram\": \"my client\", \"from\": 3686, \"to\": 3695}, {\"ngram\": \"the sponsor\", \"from\": 3700, \"to\": 37